{"tid":171351,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(絕緣暴風雨作者另一力作)(奇異x推理)虛構推理","createTime":"2017-03-25T09:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T16:56:52.000Z","uid":6327,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9b6db9eea2a645eb5fab98437a5774dd2f9a9775","tid":171351,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T09:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/25/164436_850e60f958cd9d0ca3e51305d5046869.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F25%2F164436_850e60f958cd9d0ca3e51305d5046869.jpg&h=aaa2a3fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n故事雖然係推理為題....但同一般既推理作品唔同既係<br />\n呢套野唔係單元式作品 而係圍繞住「一件事」發展<br />\n而男女主既背景會令人覺得究竟呢套係咪一套推理漫畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同暴風雨好似...都係混入左一d非現實元素<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">重點係將一d不科學靈異既事件用一個虛構既解釋去說服正常人</span><br />\n姐係類似明明有鬼都要用其他唔嚇人既方式解釋<br />\n<br />\n女主：因童年時一次事件導致左眼被挖出 右腳被切斷。第一集已經向男主求婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n男主：廢事劇透 同一個日本典故有關<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/25/164815_682aa368bc439208e59f4e4382699d6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F25%2F164815_682aa368bc439208e59f4e4382699d6a.jpg&h=95cf5fe3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/160sV27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F160sV27.jpg&h=8cd76521&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e13951e8d877fa4f8680dbe76f5d047beea5ede8","tid":171351,"uid":62714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T09:03:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實暴風雨都無乜推理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比盡話係懸疑動作片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a14ceab89a114d7c203eedb6adf3dfc985dbe524","tid":171351,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T09:07:22.000Z","msg":"樓主知咩叫推理嗎?"},{"pid":"37565486acbc1aa4f4b9b715246afae460f35ac0","tid":171351,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T09:10:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實暴風雨都無乜推理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比盡話係懸疑動作片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實真正推理其實都係推理絕園魔法師係乜水<br />\n更多既係「假推理」我覺得好正....講到似層層其實全部人係到9up但又合理先好野"},{"pid":"a30b28ce8bdff3c7a96c26144c024ad4f9ea6c7c","tid":171351,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T09:10:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主知咩叫推理嗎?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢套講到明係9up推理"},{"pid":"8d07ebd061f8425d4cdb69f6a8ba1771cf710db1","tid":171351,"uid":58120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T09:41:10.000Z","msg":"呢套我買埋單行本, 集集80幾頁真係唔買唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5232f6d9cbf62215903d546719be3bf593e7e5","tid":171351,"uid":29297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T09:47:27.000Z","msg":"識睇梗係睇埋城平京之前套少年偵探 推理之絆 同佢嘅前傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n保證屌一聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d343fd9ff5518331e98c79a0b1df111abfc1405c","tid":171351,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T09:47:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢套我買埋單行本, 集集80幾頁真係