":34760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:34:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小說漫畫化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係通常都出得好慢架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會唔會出出下又唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔會 keep住更新 <br />\n一話成七八十頁</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一齊睇</blockquote><br />\n完左架啦 小說得一本 一個故事 漫畫下一話就講哂原作所有野<br />\n小說本身應該無諗住系列化 漫畫唔知會唔會原創落去 無就完"},{"pid":"1c3b3166f122325de725725ae783049bc7d4aeb1","tid":171351,"uid":34760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:37:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>識睇梗係睇埋城平京之前套少年偵探 推理之絆 同佢嘅前傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n保證屌一聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n正面定負面先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n劇情高潮迭起 新奇有趣 保證實會嚇你一跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n城平京自己都喺後記寫係套作品臨完時先突然改部分重要設定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n前傳無睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n城京平同水野英多新果套天賀井同學比想象中普通都係一般般 難長keep落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a5e0f38e9226bd09661fbe6e8e5e4f41e7e4bf","tid":171351,"uid":91931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T18:41:07.000Z","msg":"唔係話絕園唔好睇<br />\n只係真相太令我失望<br />\n怕又係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d58c2ff37268ceae0b8b50fbf58f8605463fa0e","tid":171351,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T19:08:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>識睇梗係睇埋城平京之前套少年偵探 推理之絆 同佢嘅前傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"